{"tid":1243993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非支持者應該做的事！","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T18:19:00.000Z","uid":213059,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf2a08b47c7914822a819107c8c1ac3aefbef8b","tid":1243993,"uid":213059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"十二號嗰日我地係真係撼動到呢個政權 <br />\n令佢地暫緩！但我地未滿足 <br />\n咁我地就行動再升級 <br />\n<br />\n唔敢衝嘅 和理非嘅 唔該你地係後面充撐人數又好 運送物資又好 <br />\n但千其唔好再用咩抗爭道德 光環去綁架我地前線嘅人 <br />\n真係好動搖軍心 <br />\n我因為係前線識到好多義士 每一個都係不顧性命出嚟拋頭露面 灑熱血 <br />\n我哋唔介意你哋唔上前幫手沖 只要唔好割席同譴責 我地就心滿意足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/305k8Kg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F305k8Kg.png&h=fa5f965a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrAUtKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrAUtKg.png&h=6dd6a26f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"595ee7ab6b75289d821a22318d7240034ef701cc","tid":1243993,"uid":213059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcae5b585e24cc2965d54d4fd0c658cb583a209","tid":1243993,"uid":213059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}